  characterName: Dr. Sturgeon
  characterPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3cadb61783a8ad44abb478954be17e5d, type: 3}
  lines:
  - '*sniff*'
  - Mmmmmm...
  - MMMMMmmmmmmm....
  - MmmmmmMMMMmmmmUghhh..
  - You smell good. Too good.
  - Way too good for your own good.
  - You got a fine pair of cheeks on you too. Your getting me excited over here Mr.
  - Your making me feel...
  - Inspired.
  - My name is Dr. Sturgeon. I am the surgeon here in Westport.
  - If your here to fish go talk to Perch in his shop.
  - I sure hope you fish as good as you look. Wouldn't want to miss Perch's daily
    quotas.
  - Hop those shiny white cheeks down to Perch before I lose control of my good nature.
  textSpeed: 30
  typingSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f5d143911732a1f43b570748ed2458a4, type: 3}
